Initialize dev environment:
----------------------
1) Create virtualenv
   $ python3 -m venv venv
   $ source venv/bin/activate

2) Install packages
   $ pip install -e .


Load dev environment:
-----------------------
Load virtualenv:
$ source virtualenv/bin/activate


Run tests:
-----------------------
$ python3 -m unittest


Upload to pip:
-----------------------
$ pip install twine wheel
$ rm -rf dist
$ python3 setup.py sdist
$ python3 setup.py bdist_wheel
$ twine upload dist/*
